rong></p><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17pt;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">TensorFlow Core</strong></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1958ff-7fff-f1db-02c0-4d5ec624371b\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11pt;\">This controls the factors that serve (using the TensorFlow Serving API):</span></strong></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 11pt;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1958ff-7fff-f1db-02c0-4d5ec624371b\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11pt;\">Lifecycle</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 11pt;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1958ff-7fff-f1db-02c0-4d5ec624371b\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11pt;\">Metrics</span></strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; font-size: 11pt;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1958ff-7fff-f1db-02c0-4d5ec624371b\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11pt;\">TensorFlow Serving Core treats serves and loaders as opaque objects.</span></strong></p></li></ul><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17pt;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Life of a Servable</strong></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-8c1958ff-7fff-f1db-02c0-4d5ec624371b\"><span style=\"font-family: Aria